column100:
EVENTFORCE RETAIL is looking part time workers, who are interested in working during the night, two nights a week 
 Slagelse 
 The work consists in stocking goods in stores, Teams are working through the night  typically from 23:00 to 07:00 
   
   
 The night person: 
 -                    Is hard working 
 -                    Flexible 
 -                    Responsible 
 -                    Has the right mindset to work both in teams and on your own 
 -                    Can communicate in English 
   
 for students approx. 2 nights / week, which means good opportunity to apply for SU. 
   
 Fulltime is also possible 
   
 Working hours from 23:00 to 07:00. Both during the weekdays and weekends 
   
 If interested, please send your application and CV as soon as possible to  skbjob@eventforce.dk  - mark it “Application Eventforce”
